OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Don Howkins
OL,5,FDon Howkins, Age 102, Royal Artillery
OL,7,FInterviewed 24 April 2024
OL,9,FOriginally assigned to the Royal
OL,10,FBuckinghamshire Yeomanry, Don Howkins
OL,11,Fwas a dispatch rider attached to Royal
OL,12,FArtillery when he set off for Normandy
OL,13,Fon D-Day.
OL,15,FHe had suspected a military big
OL,16,Foperation was about to take place and
OL,17,Ftherefore married his sweetheart at
OL,18,Fthe beginning 1944.
