OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Don Howkins
OL,5,FHe and his colleagues had learned how
OL,6,Fto waterproof guns and equipment and
OL,7,Fhad been given special training while
OL,8,Fin Surrey to hot moving targets on
OL,9,Fland.
OL,11,FLeaving London docks on 6 June his
OL,12,Fvessel was off the coast during the
OL,13,Finvasion and he landed later on Gold
OL,14,FBeach, camping near Arromanches.
OL,16,FThe first engagement with the enemy
OL,17,Fwas a Tilly-sur-Seulles where there
OL,18,Fwas a lot of fighting and destruction.
