OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Don Howkins
OL,5,F"He was dead of course but he was
OL,6,Fsitting upright - shot through the
OL,7,Fhead by the infantry.
OL,9,F"You have got to remember that the
OL,10,FGerman soldiers they were good
OL,11,Fsoldiers, only youngsters like myself.
OL,12,FSomebody's son or husband.
OL,14,F"And there they all were lying dead."
OL,16,FMr Howkins continued to advance with
OL,17,Fhis unit through Belgium and Holland
OL,18,Fand into Germany.
